 significant trend in the line widths, or\ntheir ratios, with galactocentric radius. These regional line width variations\nmay be a useful probe of changes in the local cloud environment or the\nevolutionary state of molecular clouds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Feb 2019 16:57:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-27"}
