nthe data significantly better than spherical hazes, assuming a production rate\nlimited by delivery of methane to the upper atmosphere.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Feb 2019 06:11:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-03"}
