. Our simulations show good agreement with\nprevious works, indicating the feasibility and validity of the COMSOL\nimplementation of PFM.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Feb 2019 10:27:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-18"}
