rgins. We tested\nthe 8-bit ALU for all instructions up to 2.8 GHz clock frequency.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Feb 2019 15:01:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Mar 2019 19:22:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-01"}
